<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="alternative-adj">alternative <strong><em>adj</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /ɔːl'tɜːnətɪv/    美 /ɔːl'tɜːrnətɪv/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[只用于名词前] 可供替代的；可供选择的</strong></h4>
<p>that you can use, do, etc. instead of sth else：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an <strong>alternative method</strong> of learning
其他的学习方法</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The way was blocked, so we went by an alternative road. 
这条路堵塞了，因此我们走了另一条路。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>非传统的；另类的</strong></h4>
<p>different from what is usual or traditional ：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an <strong>alternative lifestyle</strong>
另类的生活方式</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="alternative-energy">alternative energy</h3>
<p>1.<strong>替代能源 (指太阳能、风能、水能等)</strong>  </p>
<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>alternatively /ɔːl'tɜːrnətɪvli/ adv   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I could come to your house, <strong>or alternatively</strong> we could meet in town.
我可以来你家找你，或者我们也可以在城里见面。</p></div>

<h2 id="_4">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The disappearance of dinosaurs is not necessarily caused by astronomical incidents. But<strong><em>_</em></strong>explanations are hard to find.   （2017 江苏）<br />
A.alternative<br />
B.aggressive<br />
C.ambiguous<br />
D.apparent  </li>
<li>As there is less and less coal and oil, scientists are exploring new ways of making use of <strong><em>_</em></strong>_(替代能源), such as sunlight, wind and water for power and fuel.  （2009 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. A  2. alternative energy  </p></div>